<ab facs="#facs_37_r1l18"><expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr gnade <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / daʒ 
<add><ab facs="#facs_37_r1l17">wir </ab></add> <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>Lampr<ex>echt</ex></expan> groſſen . dar </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_37_r1l19">umb beſant vnd ſein red gehöret wolten <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / ſo ıſt er auf dıſʒ ʒeıt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_37_r1l20">nıht anheim bey vns <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / vvenn er <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> herheim kombt ſo wellen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_37_r1l21">wır ſein red <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hören vnd <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> / <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan> ob wır daran </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_37_r1l22">gemant <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> / Als vns denn eẅr gnade an eınr ʒettel in <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>m</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_37_r1l23">brıef <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat / vvıe der <expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu Murach den <expan>v̈beltet<ex>er</ex></expan> den er <expan>gefang<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
